WEBVTT

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:32.216
People attend a law lecture,
a TED Talk of the 14th century.

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:33.800
(Laughter)

00:05:35.280 --> 00:05:36.920
Schoolchildren play.

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:40.760
Tradesmen thrive.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:45.960
Dancers larger than life dance with joy.

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:51.920
And watching over the republic
is the winged figure Security,

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:54.016
whose banner reads,

00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:57.720
"Everyone shall go forth
freely without fear."

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:01.936
Now, what's amazing
about these images from 800 years ago